{"tid":1444222,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲又傳啦 今次係一萬","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:21:56.000Z","uid":289857,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ce42c47f27fb8845f071b1feac8a73f066394171","tid":1444222,"uid":289857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9k2Z2cg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9k2Z2cg.jpg&h=08c1012c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1。佢地新傳聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CnX7rBT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCnX7rBT.jpg&h=74e14169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2。立場新聞個po<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWPUQ3C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWPUQ3C.jpg&h=86b2be6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖3。條友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係立場見到依個人share<br />\n好奇就八卦下<br />\n哇 佢地傳一萬蚊一個<br />\n搵人計下條數 由69到依家要比幾多錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真個大台比咁多錢嘅話大家點解咁少gear<br />\n貪椒好食咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次仲講緊8000 今次一萬<br />\n怪唔之得藍絲自己咁少人啦<br />\n何大哥邊比得起錢請咁多<br />\n佢地人工真係高<br />\n真係有時都忍唔住睇黎做笑料開心下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fd26c6f0dad6f2e469c0ff4fbfba8eb25d6681","tid":1444222,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7315a5f8638d16bdc272768695c595e432dc4161","tid":1444222,"uid":261885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:51:03.000Z","msg":"不如吹大d 1000萬一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7227e625a2442969f2a244a6bc8e878886859d6c"